\rho(g)(\alpha m + \beta m') = \rho(g)((\alpha 1_G)m + (\beta 1_G)m')
= (1_Fg)((\alpha 1_G)m + (\beta 1_G)m) = (1_Fg)((\alpha 1_G)m) + (1_Fg)((\beta 1_G)m')
