 = (\alpha 1_G)((1_Fg)m) + (\beta 1_G)((1_Fg)m') = (\alpha 1_G)(\rho(g)(m)) + (\beta 1_G)(\rho(g)(m'))
 = \alpha(\rho(g)(m)) + \beta(\rho(g)(m'))
